room_title: Escape room "The Jungle" by Amarillo Escape and Mystery in Amarillo
room_description: You gave your team of archaeologists two jobs, excavate the artifacts and hurry back. However, now the team is lost, or captured, or perhaps worse, dead. This leaves you no choice but to strap on your hiking boots, find your team and finish the job yourself. The problem is, your team isn’t the first to disappear in this jungle. If you go, what’s the possibility that you will ever return?
